{"word":"G5616 - ὡσεί - hōseí - ho-si' - About","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὡσεί</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hōseí</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ho-si'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">About</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"போல, ஏறக்குறைய - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"as if,"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5613 - ὡς - hōs - hoce/5613\">G5613</a> and <a href=\"#/G1487 - εἰ - ei - i/1487\">G1487</a>; <i>as if:</i> - about, as (it had been, it were), like (as).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}